{"tid":962946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本動漫產業去年產值達2兆日圓 創歷史新高","createTime":"2018-12-31T08:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T11:55:47.000Z","uid":25345,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"18930522b68f590769a11329c9aa0d46ee7a9c93","tid":962946,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://times.hinet.net/news/cimages/22/12/22126251/s_ae72a071-a69d-40f4-ac1d-8da23950c337.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimes.hinet.net%2Fnews%2Fcimages%2F22%2F12%2F22126251%2Fs_ae72a071-a69d-40f4-ac1d-8da23950c337.jpg&h=916690c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喜歡日本動漫嗎？媒體報導，日本去年動漫產業總產值，來到2兆1500億日圓，創下歷史新高。<br />\n<br />\n日本《NHK》報導，「日本動畫協會」發佈調查結果顯示，日本去年動漫產業總產值，來到2兆1527億日圓，比前年高出1600億日圓，創下歷史新高。<br />\n<br />\n報導介紹，在這2兆1527億日圓中，電影及動漫遊戲等「海外拓展」，佔了9948億日圓，而動漫角色玩偶等「商品化」，則佔了5232億日圓。<br />\n<br />\n《NHK》報導，日本動漫產業總產值創新高的主要原因，除了國外流行動漫相關的遊戲外，線上收看服務日益普及，也是關鍵因素。"},{"pid":"5921ccb6c5ec5343111449adf5f1b7d31f4e359c","tid":962946,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:01:44.000Z","msg":"糞便卻愈來愈多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f9ec4f920cedd3327a81da7894f4aca7af4653","tid":962946,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:03:40.000Z","msg":"計埋fgo果D?"},{"pid":"40a7bea6a16aa59d260eeb75512ba8bfc853a719","tid":962946,"uid":74778,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:06:07.000Z","msg":"只要日本人畫果項運動既漫畫，就會出到果項運動既世界級運動員<br />\n<br />\n例如足球小將、羽生結弦、網球王子<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e507e60ef8e99056d6912f2aa3ce60db43cbf8","tid":962946,"uid":39840,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:07:06.000Z","msg":"賺幾多都冇用,<br />\n幾時先捨得改善動畫師既待遇,<br />\n動畫業最具核心價值既一群人反而待遇最差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\"